ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This course has a strong focus on international trade, i would only recommend it to students interested in that field.
Would not recommend to other students. Selection of topics incomplete and presentation is halfhearted.
I would make a recommendation based on what the fellow student thinks of DSGE models. Depending on this she might find the course to be insightful or not.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: i didn't really know much about this field, so a good intro
It made me more sceptic of our profession's tools.
